title: Drive Into History! Old Stagecoach Stop 21159
text:
Drive Into History! Old Stagecoach Stop 21159 ad date: 10/24/2015 
Old Stagecoach Stop 21159 Carpenterville Road, Brookings 5 BR, 2 BA, 2,780 sq. ft. charming home on 17 pristine acres. Sunny country kitchen has sliders to large deck with sweeping views including Indian Mountain. Newer oversized 3 car garage with shop. Rolling hills, fruit trees, 2 water sources, vintage smoke house, plus RV/ barn and pastures. No. 15482041 $475,000 Sarah Pettinger
